{"tid":2079042,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"[年經]求打機headset推介","createTime":"2020-06-25T13:32:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-01T03:01:05.000Z","uid":157514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"88c25dd951de64fc4a09707dd3f71b6bf9e9eff5","tid":2079042,"uid":157514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T13:32:28.000Z","msg":"budget ~ 1500$樓下 平時50%時間上網睇下野聽歌睇動畫咁 50%時間打機(25%打FPS 25%打RPG類型)<br />\n岩岩爬左陣文 睇到比較多人推sennheiser 所以搵到呢幾隻選擇(爬文睇到太多型號 有D已經唔記得左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\ngame one<br />\ngame zero<br />\ngsp600<br />\ngsp550<br />\npc37x<br />\nastro a40<br />\ngame one/game zero 之前就成日睇到好多人推 話打fps一流 腳步聲方位幾準 但係音質就麻麻地咁,有d人又話game one/game zero 其實都唔係好準<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\ngsp600/gsp550 就好似同game one/game zero差唔多準 但係音質就好d 但係缺點好似係比較大舊同重 戴得耐耳仔會唔舒服 同埋價錢都比較貴<br />\n<br />\npc37x  性價比高 上網睇話呢隻就等於hd598 但係缺點香港無得買 要上網買+無保養<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nastro a40 呢隻都係以前就睇到好多人推 但係睇到有人就講以前a40呢個價位無而家咁多選擇 所以的確係幾好 但係而家多左好多選擇 a40已經係過氣產品 性價比極低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同埋我見到買a40通常都會買埋個MixAmp Pro TR 咁樣就over budget <br />\n<br />\n暫時黎講最有興趣就係pc37x 想問下各位巴打既意見 或者有無更好既選擇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"244d4c4e9192118d8dbfa0ea211dddb57b73b9c0","tid":2079042,"uid":61077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T13:42:31.000Z","msg":"pc37x 夠玩<br />\n想再好聽啲就用1500買studio headphone+支咪"},{"pid":"55772aa571c42748cd383fde8fa6e1d829166f93","tid":2079042,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T13:50:57.000Z","msg":"加多少gsp 670"},{"pid":"2f4665d14077eb053c11e3568bcc9440c4b1b818","tid":2079042,"uid":157514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"244d4c4e9192118d8dbfa0ea211dddb57b73b9c0","tid":2079042,